```
@Test    
public void whenUsingJmimeMagic_thenSuccess() {
    File file = new File("product.png");
    Magic magic = new Magic();
    MagicMatch match = magic.getMagicMatch(file, false);

    assertEquals(match.getMimeType(), "image/png");
}
```

